title: Some Dollarydoo's good sir?
body:
So apparently there is a petition to change our currency to dollarydoos and has even been on nine news.

http://www.9news.com.au/national/2015/10/16/15/39/aussies-get-behind-proposal-to-change-currency-to-dollarydoos

https://www.change.org/p/change-the-australian-currency-name-to-dollarydoos

Is this actually how retarded this country is?
